# Kratos v3 Conventions

## Module name pattern

```
github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/app/{service}
```

## Layer structure

Mỗi service follow layout Kratos chuẩn:

```
app/{service}/
├── cmd/{service}/
│   ├── main.go              # Entrypoint
│   ├── wire.go              # Wire DI providers
│   └── wire_gen.go          # Generated Wire code
├── internal/
│   ├── conf/                # Config proto → conf.pb.go
│   ├── server/              # HTTP + gRPC server bootstrap
│   ├── service/             # Proto server impl (transport)
│   ├── biz/                 # Domain logic, entities, repo interfaces
│   └── data/                # Repository implementations (sqlc, publisher, cache)
├── configs/                 # Kratos config YAML
├── Dockerfile
└── go.mod
```

## Auth middleware (shared — `pkg/auth/`)

Tất cả backend service (trừ auth) dùng `pkg/auth/` cho **opaque Bearer session introspect** (Limen):

```go
import authpkg "github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/pkg/auth"

// Trong main.go:
sessionValidator := authpkg.InitAuth(bc.Auth.AuthServiceUrl)

// Trong http.go server options:
http.Filter(authpkg.Middleware(authpkg.MiddlewareConfig{
    PublicPaths: bc.Auth.PublicPaths,
    Validator:   sessionValidator,
}))

// Trong service layer:
userID, _ := auth.UserIDFromContext(ctx)
roles, _ := auth.RolesFromContext(ctx)
auth.HasRole(ctx, "admin")
```

`auth.auth_service_url` trỏ tới auth-service (vd. `http://auth-service.puchi-backend:8000`).
Không fetch JWKS — gọi `GET /internal/session` (+ cache ~60s).

## Coding rules

- **Service layer**: Validate input, ko business logic
- **Biz layer**: Domain logic, định nghĩa repository interface
- **Data layer**: Implement repository (sqlc, pgx/v5, redis client, nats publisher)
- **Wire**: Dùng compile-time DI, ko có `init()` pattern
- **Error**: Dùng sentinel errors (`errors.New`), kiểm tra với `errors.Is()`. Ko leak internal error ra client.
- **Logger**: Dùng `log/slog` (Kratos v3 standard)
- **Config**: Đọc từ `configs/config.yaml`, parse bằng proto

## NATS Events (Outbox Pattern)

- Service emit event → ghi vào `auth.outbox` table (transactional)
- Publisher goroutine poll outbox (5s) → publish to NATS
- Subject pattern: `auth.{domain}.{event}` (ví dụ: `auth.user.created`)
- Email: publish `email.send` → notification-service handle SMTP

## sqlc + goose

- Dùng `goose` cho migration
- File migration: `migrations/` ở mỗi service
- Dùng `sqlc` generate type-safe Go code từ SQL
- `sqlc.yaml`: engine postgresql, sql_package pgx/v5, emit_interface=true

## PostgreSQL 18 features

- Dùng `uuidv7()` cho PK của bảng có time-range query (sessions, audit_logs, outbox)
- Schema riêng (`auth.*`, `core.*`) — mỗi service sở hữu schema của mình
